description:
A comprehensive ASP.NET Core template implementing Domain-Driven Design (DDD) with a focus on Vertical Slice Architecture.
            Designed for building scalable and maintainable web applications, it promotes clean separation of concerns and a modular structure for easy development and testing.
            This template also supports creating projects with React UI integrated.
            Ideal for developers looking to adopt DDD principles in their ASP.NET Core projects.
releaseNotes:
Featuring a fully structured ASP.NET Core solution with Domain-Driven Design and Vertical Slice Architecture. 
            Includes examples and ready-to-use configurations for immediate project setup.
            Added support for optional React UI integration.
title: ASP.NET Core Domain Driven Vertical Slices
